  "tiles": {
    "0": {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "# 📣 Marketing — Digital Engagement & Conversion Dashboard\n\n**Application:** [APP_NAME] (`APPLICATION-XXXXXXXXXXXX`) | **Data Source:** Gen 3 RUM (`user.events`, `user.sessions`)\n\n**[CLIENT_NAME] — Company — Company Objectives Tracked:**\n\n| Objective | KPIs on this Dashboard |\n|-----------|------------------------|\n| **Drive Online Revenue** | Booking conversion rate, daily confirmations, funnel drop-off |\n| **Grow Membership Membership** | Memberships page sessions, engagement |\n| **Increase Visitor Engagement** | Total sessions, pages per session, session duration |\n| **Optimise Multi-Channel Experience** | Device breakdown, geographic reach, browser distribution |\n| **Reduce Booking Abandonment** | Funnel step-by-step drop-off %, device-specific conversion |\n\n> **Usage:** Use this dashboard to monitor campaign effectiveness, identify where visitors drop off in the booking journey, and understand audience composition. Timeframe defaults to 7 days — adjust for campaign analysis periods."
    },
